org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker

Class ReaderWriterComponentTokenTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.BasicComponentTokenTracker
      • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.ReaderWriterComponentTokenTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentTokenTracker

    public class ReaderWriterComponentTokenTracker
extends BasicComponentTokenTracker
    Simple token tracker which frees all incoming tokens and initializes all outgoing tokens. No relation between whichever tokens is created.
